    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that it's not recommended but i'm just wondering about the actual mechanism. if i only have one small glass of wine, is the risk really that high? it feels like it would just help me drift off faster since they work on the same thing. like, would it be okay to just do it occasionally if i'm having a really bad night?",
